Iterable<com.google.gwt.user.client.ui.Widget>

    public class MaterialFileUploader
extends gwt.material.design.client.base.MaterialWidget
implements gwt.material.design.client.base.JsLoader, HasFileUpload<UploadFile>
    Custom file uploader with Dnd support with the help of dropzone.js. It has multiple feature just like the GWT File Uploader core widget.

    XML Namespace Declaration

     
 xmlns:ma='urn:import:gwt.material.design.addins.client'

    UiBinder Usage:

     
 <ma:fileuploader.MaterialFileUploader url="/file/upload"/>
    Author:
    kevzlou7979
    See Also:
    File Uploader, Dropzone 4.3.0
